	of
	
	supernatural
	
	entities
	
	and
	uses
	object-fronting</p>
	<p>
	to
	mark
	the
	exception
	to
	this
	denial,
	as
	soon
	as
	it
	is
	brought
	to
	his
	attention.</p>
	<p>
	Predicate-fronting
	occurs
	when
	a
	predicate
	that
	contains
	new
	information
	is
	introduced
	in
	conjunction
	with
	a
	subject
	which
	has
