	the way that
	creoles handle
	articles. Virtually
	all
	creoles
	have a
	system iden&shy;
	tical to
	that of
	HCE: a
	definite article
	for presupposed-specific
	NP; an indefinite
	article for
	asserted-specific NP;
	and zero
	for nonspecific
	NP.
