	I hear
	beating?</p>
	<p>
	/145/
	The drums
	that I
	heard beating
	never stopped.</p>
	<p>
	<br/>

	</p>
	<p>
	Extraction  from
	the circled 
	node  of
	/ 141/,
	however, yields
	only sen-.
	tences which
	are ungrammatical
	in GC:</p>
	<p>
	<br/>

