	<p>
	/163/
	i
	tel
	mi
	se
	ina
	si
	am</p>
	<p>
	'He told
	me that
	he didn't see
	it'</p>
	<p>
	/164/
	mi no
	se ina
	si am</p>
	<p>
	'I know
	that he
	didn't see
	it'</p>
