	<p>
	<br/>

	</p>
	<p>
	nouns, verbs,
	and very
	little else.
	They assume
	that VP
	is a
	pidgin category, but
	do not
	defend it
	as such.
	For reasons
	given in
	the dis&shy;
	cussion of
	GC movement
