</p>
<div id="Bereich142" dir="ltr" gutter="39" style="column-count: 2">
	<p>
	<sub>1</sub><sub>50	</sub>ROOTS
	OF LANGUAGE</p>
	<p>
	<br/>

	</p>
	<p>
	zero, represent
	two
	distinctions-supposed-known-to-listener
	<i>I
	</i>sup&shy;
	posed-unknown-to-listener
	and specific-referent
	<i>I
	</i>no-specific-referent&shy; but
