	distinguish  specific
	 from 
	nonspecific  <i>a.
	
	</i>One  might
	think he
	could do
	this by
	distinguishing between
	 linguistic 
	environ&shy; ments. For
	instance,  the 
	scope of 
	negation  is
	often  crucial
	in determin&shy;
	ing whether
	a given
	occurrence of
	<i>a
	NP
	</i>is specific
