	that
	the
	child
	invariably
	forms
	
	a
	
	correct
	
	hypothesis
	
	about
	
	the
	
	SNSD
	as
	his
	first
	hypothesis
	is
	simply
	an
	issue-dodging
	way
	of
	saying
	that
	he
	is
