	ACQUISITION<sub>	</sub><sub>2</sub><sub>0</sub><sub>9</sub></p>
	<p>
	There are
	so many
	replies
	to this,
	one hardly
	knows  where 
	to start.
	Let me
	begin by
	saying that
	students of
