	the right-hand
	side because
	there aren't
	any streetlamps.
	on the
	left·hand
	side.
	Further, the
	claim that
	the theory is
	untestable, like
	the claim
	that innateness
	represents a
	necessary terminus for
	research, is
	simply untrue.</p>
