	<p>
	<br/>

	</p>
	<p>
	The  first 
	of  the 
	semantic  areas
	I shall
	touch  on
	concerns predica&shy;
	tions which 
	may  be 
	felt  to 
	be  central
	in
	any 
	structured  language
	 sys, tern: 
	<i>There 
	is
	an
	X
