	</i>X,
	<i>X
	
	is
	Z's.
	
	</i>I shall
	refer to
	the relationships 
	expressed  by 
	these  predications
	 as
	Existence, Lc&gt;ca.tl&lt;m;&gt;J'</p>
	<p>
	Possession,  and 
	Ownership.  Ishould
	emphasize that
	these labels</p>
	<p>
	chosen only
	for convenience
	of reference
	and are
	not meant
	to nave
	&lt;l!''. any  particular
