	at the</p>
	<p>
	same time
	as the
	development of
	displacement. If
	I report what
	another person said
	and that
	other person
	is not
	present, then
	obviously the
	saying must
	have occurred
	on a
	previous occasion.
	If I
	tell you
	<i>Ug
	say
	honey
	here,
	</i>it
	requires no
	Socratic intellect
	to figure
