	parsing problems
	arising from
	case assignment.
	Some scaffolding
	is required
	that will
	accurately fix
	the place
	of sentences
	in the
	world of time
	and reality; TMA
	systems supply
	this scaffolding.</p>
	<p>
	Quine (1960:
