		which explicitly
		recognize the
		absence of
		the characteristic
		Western temporal
		framework. Analysis
		of TMA
		systems is too
		subtle to be
		left to
		logicians.</p>
	</ol>
	<ol start="12">
		<li/>
<p>In
		Bickerton 1974.</p>
		<li/>
